聆听忠实的“合成器浸泡的新单曲”的“和平与噪音” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-fihtless-synth-synth-synth-synth-single-new-single-peace-noise-noise-3848195?utm_source = rsss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = listm_campaign = listcampaign=listen=listente-faith-new-new-new-new-new-singlePoppy Burton Fri, 21 Mar 2025 13:36:30 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3848195 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="毫无忠诚" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “一个小宝石，使每个人都为即将发行的专辑&#39;Champion Sound&#39;的温暖和天才而温暖。</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-faithless-synth-soaked-new-single-peace-noise-3848195">聆听了不忠的“合成器浸泡的新单曲”“和平与噪音”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="毫无忠诚" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-faithless-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faithless">忠实的人</a>分享了他们合成器浸泡的新单曲“和平与噪音”  - 在下面的曲调。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-interview-sister-bliss-maxi-jazz-champion-sound-not-alone-tour-3789161">不忠实的谈话来纪念马克西爵士乐和未来：“这是情感和礼物”</a></strong></li></ul><p>英国舞蹈先驱者今天（3月21日）分享了一个有力的新房子，“和平与噪音”，其中包括口语艺术家Suli Breaks。</p><p>该曲目标志着他们2025年的第一首新音乐，并在最近的单曲“找到方法”和“我并不孤单（REST Well Maxwell）”之后。它还进行了旋风12个月的现场表演，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-announce-2024-champion-sound-uk-and-european-tour-3787512">欧洲巡回演出</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-fatboy-slim-camelphat-groove-armada-lead-glastonbury-2024-glade-area-line-up-3749471">格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）的老虎机</a>。</p><p>乐队在新闻稿中讨论最新歌曲时说：“ Suli Breaks是我们上一张专辑的明星，在这里，他再次提供了抒情内容，既是平淡又深刻的抒情内容，加深了这首曲目的时髦rowdiness，本身就是一个小宝石，可以使每个人都为即将出现的专辑的冠军声音，冠军声音的温暖和天才而温暖。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="忠诚 - 和平与噪音（苏利岛破裂）（官方的Visualiser）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-YXx8WZMAaE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>去年，Faveless宣布了他们的第八张专辑“ Champion Sound”，尽管尚未确认发行日期。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-announce-eighth-album-champion-sound-with-funky-new-single-find-a-way-3774503">宣布了即将发行的专辑，并带有主打单曲“ Find Away</a> ”之后，“我并不孤单”标志着他们自2020年代以来的首款新音乐，也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-share-details-of-all-blessed-their-first-new-album-in-a-decade-2740394">标志着</a>自2022年12月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-singer-maxi-jazz-died-aged-65-3371280">的主持人Maxi Jazz逝世</a>以来，他们也是他们的第一部发行。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-interview-sister-bliss-maxi-jazz-champion-sound-not-alone-tour-3789161">布利斯姐妹（Sister Bliss）与<em>NME</em>谈到了下一张专辑</a>，当时，她和乐队仍在继续工作。她说：“目前，我们处于一种极大的创意模式。” “前几天，当我们从一位合作者那里发声时，我感到非常兴奋，以至于我真的感到恶心。</p><p> “我觉得这是可以解锁专辑的钥匙之一……不是任何人都对专辑蒙上了一声，而是我们这样做了，也许我们的粉丝也这样做了。”</p><p>舞蹈先驱说，制作新唱片“是使新人们以集体和协作的方式使新人们陷入忠诚的平台”。</p><p>她补充说，找到标题有助于传达信息：“我觉得&#39;Champion Sound&#39;确实描述了我们在做什么。它具有粗糙度，DIY，合作感，这是基于声音系统能量史的基础。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHdSufaN7KV/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 