p-content/uploads/2025/03/live-drake-kendrick-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-drake-kendrick-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-drake-kendrick-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-drake-kendrick-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Drake">德雷克</a>（Drake）的律师声称，“数百万人”认为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Kendrick-Lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）</a>实际上称他为恋童癖者。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820"><b>Drake和Kendrick Lamar的仇恨：完整的时间表</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>去年11月，“热线蓝调”杀手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-kendrick-lamar-not-like-us-universal-spotify-artificially-inflated-allegation-3815805">在纽约对环球音乐集团提出了争执，称出版商和标签对“不喜欢我们”的“人为膨胀”流了其他指控</a>。</p><p>在备案中 - <a href="https://iapps.courts.state.ny.us/nyscef/ViewDocument?docIndex=JV6RsbXQWW1I6Jol1X1qNA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可以在这里查看</a>- 德雷克（Drake）的《冷冻时刻》有限责任公司（Frozen Misments LLC）被指控UMG，并在去年与德雷克（Drake）进行了病毒说唱仇恨，并促进了“非法”协助和增强“不喜欢我们”的溪流。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/umg-say-drake-lost-rap-battle-with-kendrick-lamar-in-scathing-legal-motion-he-has-sued-his-own-record-label-in-a-misguided-attempt-to-salve-his-wounds-3847315">UMG提出了一项动议，以驳回加拿大说唱歌手的诉讼，并指出他起诉了该公司，因为他“失去了说唱战”</a> 。他们接着说：“德雷克没有像他经常声称自己那样的不受欢迎的说唱艺术家那样接受损失。”德雷克“起诉了自己的唱片公司，以误解了伤口的误导”。</p><p> UMG还列举了2022年的请愿书，指出德雷克与其他各种音乐家一起敦促检察官停止以说唱歌词为刑事审判的证据。 “德雷克当时是对的，现在是错的，”备案写道。 “投诉对UMG的不合理主张只不过是德雷克试图为他与拉马尔的说唱战斗失败而挽救面孔。” </p><figure id="attachment_3838205" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3838205" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3838205" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drake-2000x1270-Cole-Burston_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="德雷克。图片来源：Cole Burston/Getty Images。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drake-2000x1270-Cole-Burston_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drake-2000x1270-Cole-Burston_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drake-2000x1270-Cole-Burston_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drake-2000x1270-Cole-Burston_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drake-2000x1270-Cole-Burston_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/drake-2000x1270-Cole-Burston_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3838205" class="wp-caption-text">德雷克。图片来源：Cole Burston/Getty Images。</figcaption></figure><p>昨天（3月20日），德雷克（Drake）的团队对UMG的中心论点进行了反击：大多数听众不会接受“令人发指的侮辱”，这在Diss曲目中自然是相当的。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/drake-umg-lawsuit-rapper-lawyers-kendrick-literally/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>广告牌</em></a>，“传奇”说唱歌手的律师说，论点“注定要失败”，因为人们认真对待了拉马尔的话。</p><p>他的律师写道：“ UMG完全忽略了投诉的指控，即世界各地数百万的人确实将诽谤性材料理解为事实上的断言，即原告是恋童癖者。”</p><p>的确，拉马尔（Lamar）在2月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kendrick-lamar-full-2025-super-bowl-halftime-show-3836498">的超级碗Lix半场表演中担任了</a>音乐中最大的13分钟演出。拥有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> ，Serena Williams和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">Samuel L. Jackson</a>的来宾露面，后来被评为历史上观看最多的超级碗表演，并看到了有争议的曲目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3837602" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837602" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837602" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World.jpg" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）在超级碗舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837602" class="wp-caption-text">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）在超级碗比赛中现场表演。图片来源：迈克尔·欧文斯/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>它还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-spawns-new-meme-with-not-like-us-at-super-bowl-2025-3836462">在社交媒体上产生了一个新的模因</a>，许多人注意到肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）在丢下“不喜欢我们”的台词时，对镜头笑了笑：“<em>说德雷克，我听到你喜欢&#39;em Young&#39;</em> 。</p><p>德雷克（Drake）的律师继续说：“ umg也忽略了[诉讼的说法]，即所讨论的陈述（以及周围背景）暗示指控是基于未公开的证据，听众也理解了很多。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/umg-say-drake-lost-rap-battle-with-kendrick-lamar-in-scathing-legal-motion-he-has-sued-his-own-record-label-in-a-misguided-attempt-to-salve-his-wounds-3847315"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在其他地方，德雷克（Drake）最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-has-settled-his-payola-dispute-with-iheartmedia-for-promoting-kendrick-lamars-not-like-us-3843310">解决了他对伊哈特媒体（Iheartmedia）的佩吉拉（Payola）争端，因为他宣传了“不像我们”。</a></p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drakes-lawyers-claim-millions-of-people-believe-kendrick-lamar-was-literally-calling-him-a-pedophile-3848148">德雷克邮报的律师声称“数百万人”认为肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）实际上称他为恋